displaced vertices\nreconstructed and matched with jets. The performance of this method is\ndetermined using a dijet calibration dataset recorded by the LHCb detector and\nselected such that the jets are unbiased in quantities used in the tagging\nalgorithm. The charm-tagging efficiency is reported as a function of the\ntransverse momentum of the jet. The measured efficiencies are compared to those\nobtained from simulation and found to be in good agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2021 19:22:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 15:41:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-25"}
