ote of a tuba in particular), whose\nbehaviour qualitatively differs from a trombone to a euphonium for instance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2021 10:06:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2022 10:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-17"}
